2. Create a trigger to handle inserts to the product relation ( if price < 5 the set price to 10).

mysql> delimiter //
mysql> create trigger products_price
    -> before insert
    -> on product
    -> for each row
    -> begin
    -> if new.price<5 then
    -> set new.price=10;
    -> end if
    -> ;
    -> end //
